State: new
Subject: Duplicate company configuration across files
Message-Id: <aff11fd7d412e9ca-0-artemis@nixos-amd64>

The `company` package is configured in multiple files:
- warbo-generic.el has a use-package company block
- warbo-rust.el also has a use-package company block (currently disabled)

This duplication should be consolidated into a single configuration location to
avoid maintenance issues and conflicting settings.
